      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this beauty. I've taken such good care of it, it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! No scratches, no dents, and the interior is absolutely spotless\u2014it even still has that fresh smell. It's been my pride and joy, but it's time for a new home. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand new price tag, this is definitely the one! Shoot me a message if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
