    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 1994 Mazda RX-7 is a pristine example of the FD3S chassis, featuring the legendary 13B-REW rotary engine with its sequential twin-turbocharger system fully intact and operating with flawless boost transition. The vehicle exhibits exceptional mechanical integrity, retaining its factory-spec double-wishbone suspension and Torsen limited-slip differential. Compression numbers are optimal across all rotor faces, reflecting a meticulous maintenance history and strictly stock configuration. Finished in its original Montego Blue, the exterior remains concours-level, while the interior shows no signs of bolster wear or dash warping. A rare, unmolested survivor with a longitudinal front-midship layout providing a perfect 50/50 weight distribution for unparalleled handling precision.",
      "price": 48500.0,
